{
  "stem": "4247.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And parties-- of course, girls were very strong part of our early interest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Most of them were Jewish girls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were some non-Jewish girls involved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No non-Jewish boys involved in that-- in that group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But as matters became by law-- because the second Jewish law and the Jewish law came in, regulated.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Social intercourse between Jews and, and non-Jews have been not only discouraged, but, but, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] but strictly inhibited by-- by law.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So much so that you couldn't marry a non-Jewish person.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You couldn't have sex with a non-Jewish person.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was all strictly and, and severely punishable, right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So in this atmosphere, our social activity was completely restricted within Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] So when I matriculated in school, because of the numerous clauses, nothing was, was open for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father, who was essentially a very practical person, said, well, you have to learn a trade.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we looked around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't very easy at the time even to get an apprenticeship for a Jewish boy because a lot of Jewish boys were out and trying to-- to do something.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We somehow managed-- pardon me-- to get a-- pardon me-- to get to an apprenticeship in a-- in a toolmaking workshop, where I have been committed for one-and-half-year apprenticeship.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Now I would like to say this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm not a particularly mechanically-minded person, never been.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I always had some ability and some inclination to follow plans and, and be-- tried to be accurate, even in manual works-- work as well.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This one and a half year was a very hard time of my life.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
